data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! Welcome to your dream lakefront retreat on Silver Lake! Nestled on an oversized lot, this charming home boasts breathtaking views and a tranquil ambiance that will captivate you from the moment you arrive. As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by a beautifully landscaped yard, providing a sense of privacy and serenity. The expansive lot allows for ample outdoor space, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying the picturesque surroundings. Step inside this delightful 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, with bonus office space and be immediately drawn to the stunning lake views showcased through large windows that fill the living area with natural light. The open concept floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it ideal for both relaxation and entertaining. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and hidden walk-in pantry. Prepare delicious meals while taking in the scenic lake vistas or gather around the dining area with loved ones to savor the flavors of your culinary creations. Outside, a large deck awaits, offering the perfect spot to relax, soak up the sun, and revel in the mesmerizing beauty of Silver Lake. Enjoy al fresco dining, host barbecues, or simply unwind while savoring the gentle breeze. A peninsula provides direct access to the water for boating, fishing, or simply taking in the tranquility of the surroundings. This lakefront oasis is conveniently located near local amenities, restaurants, and recreational activities, ensuring you have everything you need for a well-rounded lifestyle. Assumable FHA mortgage rate of 2.375% on aproximately $250K. Home is also available for Rent $2700/mo minimum 12 month lease.
